latestPosts.caption:
Started from the bottom, and now we're here!!!
Extremely honored to have won "THE LUXURY FASHION INFLUENCER OF THE YEAR AWARD" (2023 - 2024) by @dainikjagrannews @jagranicawards @jagranenglishnews .
We still remember how we didn't believe in ourselves when we started our journey 7 years a go into this digital world and now to be recognized by so many and been working with the top brands globally. 
Honestly have manifested every bit of it, worked hard so much, so much to reach here, and ofcourse the LOVE we've got from you guys...❤️ 
This Award we genuinely dedicate it to you guys coz without you guys we're nothing. 
Thanking all of you, my lovely digital family once again for showering us with so much of love and affection. 
.
Outfits- @saggarmehraofficial @saggarmehra

What an unforgettable culinary journey I experienced recently at @loya.taj . Literally every bite I took; was a journey. 
Loya transports you to a world where every meal is a celebration of heritage, culture, and flavour.
Loya celebrates the rich heritage of North Indian gastronomy, bringing together time-honored cooking techniques, heirloom ingredients, and cherished recipes in an immersive experience.
In every dish, drink, and moment, Loya redefines dining. Had one of the best dining experiences with @tajmahalmumbai @loya.taj
.
Can't wait to be there again. Thank you for having us ✨️
.
.
.
#LoyaTaj #TajMahalMumbai #Taj #SoBoGuys #AmaanArmaan
